ICMA 09/16/2025

glimpse(flights)
flights_houston <- flights |>
    filter(dest %in% c("IAH", "HOU"))
flights |>
  filter(arr_delay > 120 & dep_delay <= 0)

ICMA 9/18/25

flights |>
  group_by(month)
flights |>
  group_by(month, day) |>
  count()
flights |>
  group_by(month) |>
  summarise(mean_arr_delay = mean(arr_delay, na.rm = TRUE), 
        sd_arr_delay = sd(arr_delay, na.rm = TRUE), 
        number_delayed = sum(arr_delay > 0, na.rm = TRUE), 
        number_total = n()) |>

  mutate(percentage = number_delayed/number_total) |>
  ggplot(aes(y = percentage, x = month)) + 
  geom_line() + 
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = 1:12) + 
  ylim(0, 0.55)

head(billboard)
billboard |>
  pivot_longer(cols = wk1:wk76, 
               names_to = "week", 
               values_to = "rank") |>
  head(10)
billboard |>
  filter(artist == "2 Pac") |>
  select(artist, wk10)
billboard_long |>
  filter(artist == "2 Pac" & week == "wk10")
billboard_long_dropna <- billboard |>
  pivot_longer(cols = wk1:wk76, 
               names_to = "week", 
               values_to = "rank",
               values_drop_na = TRUE)

billboard_long_dropna |>
  filter(artist == "2 Pac " & week == "wk10")
billboard_long_dropna |>
  pivot_wider(names_from = "week", 
              values_from = "rank")
?pivot_longer

#ICMA 09/30/25

flights |>
  mutate(gain = arr_delay - dep_delay) |>
  filter(!is.na(gain)) |>
  group_by(carrier) |>
  summarize(
    avg_gain = mean(gain), 
    total_flights = n()
    ) |>
  arrange(desc(avg_gain)) |>
  select(carrier, avg_gain, total_flights)
